    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen exhibits zero rod bearing play and a documented VANOS overhaul, ensuring the high-pressure oil pump and solenoid valves operate within factory tolerances. The subframe has been proactively reinforced to mitigate chassis fatigue. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension geometry remains true, with no bushing deflection or damper seepage. Finished in concours-level paint with a pristine undercarriage, this is a turn-key enthusiast piece devoid of the typical electronic gremlins or cooling system vulnerabilities.",
      "price": 44900.0,
