      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its original showroom luster with deep, mirror-like paint clarity and zero swirl marks. The interior is in pristine condition, featuring supple, uncreased leather and a cabin that still carries a fresh, factory-new scent. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of maintenance records included. From the untouched alloy wheels to the crystal-clear headlight lenses, every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest expectations. This is a non-smoker, no-pet vehicle that has never been exposed to salt or inclement weather. For the discerning buyer seeking a turnkey vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, this car stands in a class of its own.",
